Norwegian Wood

An installation by Hellicar&Lewis.
http://hellicarandlewis.com
http://www.hellicarandlewis.com/2011/03/02/norwegian-wood/

Compatible with of_preRelease_v0062_osxSL_FAT

http://openframeworks.cc
http://openframeworks.cc/download

Thanks to the whole OpenFrameworks community.

Requires a Video Camera and Working Audio Input.

Run Norwegian Wood app to see the four interactive scenes that react to audio. Press keys 1-4 to change scenes.
Run the Shape Drawing app to draw new polygon shapes.

Uses:

The initial animation of the grass blades was based on the reach2 demo from http://processing.org which was based on code from Keith Peters. 

http://www.bit-101.com

ofxNoise by Rui Madeira 

http://ruim.pt

http://code.google.com/p/ruicode/
ofxNoise_001c.zip is the download that I used.

ofxBox2d by Todd Vanderlin

http://vanderlin.cc

https://github.com/vanderlin/ofxBox2d

ofxControlPanel by Theo Watson

http://theowatson.com/

https://github.com/ofTheo/ofxControlPanel